Over the last 5 years, MetaDoncia has taught 94 editions and a total of 388 hours of 8 different workshops. We reached 2404 educators, researchers and technicians, of which 64.8% attended synchronously and 79.6% completed the post workshop survey, in which we obtained an average Net Promoter Score (NPS) of 88.9% (min = 71.4, max = 100). This is considered excellent, as the NPS ranges from -100% to +100%, and values larger than +50%—our target—reflect very high satisfaction from the participants.

